# AI PDF Conversation App

This simple Python app, powered by AI, allows you to have a conversation with a PDF document by passing in the path of the PDF.

## Dependencies

This project uses Poetry for dependency management. To install Poetry, follow the instructions on their official website: https://python-poetry.org/docs/#installation

## Project Setup

1. Clone the repository to your local machine.

2. To install project dependencies run:
```bash
   poetry install
```

3. Activate the virtual environment created by Poetry:

```bash
poetry shell
```

## Usage

To use the app, simply pass in the path of a PDF file as an argument:

```bash
python app.py --pdf /path/to/your/pdf/document.pdf
```

This will start an interactive session where you can have a conversation with the content of the PDF.

